the cold thing is interesting because we went to auction last year actually November of 96 to get the proof letters that were finally released that were about his homosexuality and they were front page on New York Times and everything and we and actually our university librarian Bob Wedgworth told me to go ahead and try to get him and so we hired an agent and she tried to get him and the interesting story there is that
